        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>school buildings by subject [300006525], schools (buildings) [300006495], academic buildings [300444406], institutional buildings [300132384], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings that house either Hebrew-English day schools providing both secular and religious instruction, usually operated under Orthodox Jewish auspices, or for schools providing training in Talmudic law and which may ordain rabbis. For educational facilities specifically devoted to the training of rabbis, use "rabbinical seminaries." For buildings that house day schools operated under Reform or Conservative Jewish auspices, use "Hebrew schools."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Designa tanto la escuela hebreo-inglesa que proporciona instrucción secular y religiosa, generalmente gestionada por los judíos ortodoxos, como la escuela que proporciona instrucción en la ley del Talmud y que puede ordenar rabinos. Para instalaciones educacionales dedicadas específicamente a la enseñanza de los rabinos, empléese "seminario rabínico". Para escuelas gestionadas para los judíos reformistas o conservadores, empléese "escuela hebrea".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor Hebreeuws-Engelse scholen die zowel seculier als religieus onderwijs bieden, meestal bestuurd onder orthodox-joodse auspiciën, of wordt gebruikt voor scholen die onderwijs geven in de talmoedische wet en die rabbi's wijden. Gebruik 'rabbijnenscholen' voor onderwijsinstellingen die speciaal zijn bedoeld voor het scholen van rabbi's. Gebruik 'joodse scholen' voor scholen die worden bestuurd onder hervormd of conservatief joodse auspiciën.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099099/Van Dale groot woordenboek (1994)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>用來指稱希伯來文和英文並用的雙語日校，提供世俗與宗教課程，通常由正統派猶太教所開辦營運；也可指稱傳授塔木德法典的學校，修業後可被授以拉比一職。而專門培訓拉比的教育場所，使用「拉比神學院」；而由保守派或改革派猶太人士所開辦營運的日校，則使用「猶太學校」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
